While I want to see him play and win (he's awesome), it wouldn't surprise me if his documents are forged. 
I was employed as a health and safety consultant at a major int airport in Europe when covid began to majorly effect flights, and we had average Joes flying on forged tests. There's nothing you can do about it without access to a national register. One case a woman handed over a positive test and was refused boarding. The next day she came back with a negative test... we knew she was positive but there was nothing we could do, she had the paperwork...
